    * Global parametrization of Koning-Duijvestijn/17/            9861 1451
      was used.                                                   9861 1451
    * Gamma emission channel/18/ was added to simulate direct     9861 1451
      and semi-direct capture reaction.                           9861 1451
                                                                  9861 1451
